MOBILE APP DESIGN GUIDELINES
Project: Student Focus & Productivity App
Audience: College Students
Design Style: Modern ‚Ä¢ Minimal ‚Ä¢ Glassmorphism ‚Ä¢ High Clarity

‚∏ª

1. DESIGN PRINCIPLES

Clarity over decoration
Every screen should communicate purpose instantly.

Focus-driven interface
Remove visual noise. Highlight what needs attention now.

Calm but motivating
Interface should feel peaceful, not overwhelming.

Fast comprehension
Users should understand the screen within 2 seconds.

Reward progress visually
Celebrate streaks, focus sessions, and improvements.

‚∏ª

2. VISUAL STYLE

Primary Aesthetic

Modern glassmorphism + soft depth

Inspired by:
‚Ä¢ frosted glass panels
‚Ä¢ soft gradients
‚Ä¢ floating UI cards
‚Ä¢ subtle glow highlights

Use:
	‚Ä¢	translucent cards
	‚Ä¢	blurred backgrounds
	‚Ä¢	soft shadows
	‚Ä¢	layered depth

Avoid:
	‚Ä¢	heavy borders
	‚Ä¢	sharp contrasts
	‚Ä¢	cluttered layouts

‚∏ª

3. COLOR SYSTEM

Base Theme

Dark mode default (students use apps at night)

Background:
Deep charcoal / midnight blue gradient

