5. LAYOUT SYSTEM

Spacing

Use generous spacing for clarity.

8px grid system:
8 / 16 / 24 / 32 spacing increments

‚∏ª

Card Design

Cards should:
	‚Ä¢	float above background
	‚Ä¢	have rounded corners (16‚Äì20px)
	‚Ä¢	include soft shadow depth

Shadow:
0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.25)

